init_text: Your entire life, you've been told you're deathly allergic to bees. You've always had people protecting you from them, be it your mother or a hired hand. Today, one slips through and lands on your shoulder. You hear a tiny voice say "Your Majesty, what are your orders?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But you're not going to let that happen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You're going to take your rightful place as ruler of the bees.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: And you're going to do it by ordering your subjects to do what you want.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You look around, and see a hive.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The hive responds, and you hear a buzzing sound.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You've just created a distributed system.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You've also just created a distributed system that is a lot like a blockchain.

actions.name: text-delete
actions.text: You've just created a distributed system.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The blockchain is a distributed ledger.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It's a way of storing information that is shared across a network of computers.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: This ledger is updated by a consensus mechanism, so that everyone on the network knows the current state of the ledger.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They fly around the datacenter, and land on the servers.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The technician walks over to a rack of servers and gives a command.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You've just made a million dollars.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The bees have just created a new cryptocurrency.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: This is the future of blockchain.
